Q: How do I clear the screen in C++?
A: Bad:

```
#include <iostream>
#include <string>

void ClearScreen()
{
cout << string( 100, '\n' );
}
```

Q: What hardware should Car_Base.cpp run on?
A:
   - RPi Zero?
     - Standard C++ code without any extra libs.
     - Relatively low power
   - Arduino Pro Mini?
     - Requires arduino.h
     - Requires a programmer UART
   - Arduino Nano?
     - Requires arduino.h
   - Arduino Mega
     - Requires arduino.h
   - RPi4 w/ screen
     - Standard C++ code without any extra libs.
     - Requires a lot of power